-----------------------------------------------------------------------
2014 - THE YEAR IN CHRISTIAN MUSIC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------

Just as with the 50th bundle torrented earlier today, this 51st bundle also contains shares from this past month on Christian Tunes.  For anyone willing to help me seed any albums which they directly downloaded from Christian Tunes, I would greatly appreciate your help.  If you're not sure how, it's pretty simple ... (1) create a folder called "2014 - The Year In Christian Music (Bundle 51)" in the same folder where your torrents are usually downloaded to.  (2) copy and paste your downloaded music into that folder.  (3) then download the torrent as you normally would.  Your torrent client will recognize that you already have some of these albums, and instead of a downloader, you will be recognized as an uploader for those albums you just copied over.
